| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4601 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6ee25cd7-c446-5409-8c58-c90b69d30c98"
